data.description: Living the lifestyle in the sought after community of The Groves. This 2020 one-story four-sided brick home is gorgeous with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, and 2 car garage. The large island and peninsula are perfect for entertaining.  The extra bonus cabinets space is a plus. Recessed lighting throughout the living area with loads of windows for natural light. Wood tile flooring throughout the living area. Granite countertop, stainless steel appliances, and white cabinets with undermounted cabinet lights makes this open concept floorplan desirable. Primary bathroom shower has wall to ceiling tile, double vanity and separate tub and shower. Recessed lighting throughout the garage. Garage has a generator plug that's hard wired into the electrical panel with its own breaker. Compatible for portable generators. Covered patio pre-wired for ceiling fan. Sprinkler system in front and back. French drain.
